        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二老军搀薛礼同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在月下惊碎了英雄虎胆，\n思家乡回故土千难万难。\n平白地要拿我所为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周青，何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "我与那尉元帅无仇无怨、周青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张总爷过营探病。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快地有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，张士贵，叫你进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随我进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，薛礼，本帅来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓，总爷吓！小人有何德能，敢劳总爷过营探病。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你屡次抢关夺寨，理当如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢总爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，薛礼，你此病因何而起？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓，总爷吓，那日小人山神庙外，仰天看月，不料尉迟老元戎从后而来，将\n小人搂抱在怀，是小人将他推倒在地，奔命而逃。小人这病，乃是从惊唬而来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怪不得尉迟老元戎问我要你，是我花言巧语，将他瞒哄过去，从今而后，再若\n撞着于他，只恐你的性命难保。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓总爷，这几日可曾抢关夺寨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再也不要提起。大兵来到独木关，偶遇安殿宝一马挡住。你染病在床，我命二\n位少爷出马，又被他们擒去。我命中军拿了令箭，调众位英雄前去搭救，中军\n不会讲话，他们将令箭拗断，将中军暴打一顿，是我亲自过营，带了中军与他\n们陪礼。\n中军跪下。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛礼昏倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众伙头军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你将我大哥气死了。跪下叫吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫伙头军爷爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙头军爷爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众伙头军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥醒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "打中军劫令箭如同造反，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快来救我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "似这等犯王法罪可欺天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "总爷，你这算何意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我与你讲话，你一时昏迷过去，他们将我捆绑起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这还了得，快快地松绑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众伙头军同与张士贵松绑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓，总爷吓，你看小人这班兄弟，俱是不法之徒，恐小人下世，他们必要谋\n反朝庭，趁小人在世，将他们斩首，以正军规。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看在你的份上，亦要将他们饶恕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还不过来谢过总爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众伙头军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢总爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少打几下，也就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周青过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周青允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带领众位贤弟，搭救二位少爷回来，将功折罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众伙头军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众伙头军同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张士贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你好好养息，我要回营去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能奉送。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张士贵、四龙套、中军同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "张总爷过营来将我来探，"
        }
      ],
