    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二老军",
        "薛礼"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二老军搀薛礼同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一路上枪挑了无数的上将，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（起鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？哪里这样擂鼓呐喊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "教场操演。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，教场操演。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（起鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？这不像操演之声，为何这般喊杀连天？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……那个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！你二人要言不言，要语不语，是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，薛爷吓，今有周青带领众家英雄，搭救二位少爷。那辽邦又出了个大将"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，俺薛礼得下这样冤孽病症，那辽邦又出了什么大将安殿宝。也罢，待我前"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，薛爷你出马，岂是那安殿宝的对手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听一言气得我三魂飘荡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛礼",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫老军抬枪马爷到战场。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛礼下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "薛礼→二老军",
          "turns": 4
        },
        {
          "edge": "二老军→薛礼",
          "turns": 4
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
