    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "何宗宪",
        "安殿宝",
        "张志龙",
        "迈步且把宝帐踏",
        "进得帐高声骂"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同上，安殿宝上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "安殿宝",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "威风凛凛貌堂堂，虎背熊腰谁敢当。今日领动人和马，好似猛虎赶群羊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安殿宝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大将安殿宝。奉主之命，镇守独木关。昨日拿住两个死囚，未曾发落。\n来，将那两上死囚押上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手押张志龙、何宗宪同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张志龙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "龙入沙滩爪方下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "何宗宪",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "虎落平阳被犬拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张志龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军，此番进帐，还是叫骂的是，还是哀求的是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "何宗宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自然叫骂的是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张志龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哀求的是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何宗宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大舅子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "何宗宪",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大舅子休说懦弱话，\n非是姐丈把你压。\n拼得一死染黄沙。\n看你把爷怎开发。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进得帐高声骂、迈步且把宝帐踏、安殿宝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两个死囚，通名受死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张志龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃张士贵之子，名叫张志龙是也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安殿宝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一个呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "何宗宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃白袍薛礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安殿宝",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "安殿宝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道薛仁贵天上少有，地下难寻，今日一见，原来是个黄毛小子。\n来，推去斩了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何宗宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要忙，我是假充字号，我叫何宗宪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安殿宝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，将他二人绑在后面，拿住薛礼一齐开刀。押下去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张志龙、何宗宪同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "安殿宝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，杀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（安殿宝、四龙套同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
